title: Exclusive clip: Shatner guests on AMC's 'Comic Book Men'
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: TV - Today 
Kevin Smith sits down with William Shatner to talk comics, conventions and "Star Trek" in an exclusive clip from AMC's "Comic Book Men."
